text:
the person manning the store i think got attitude problem,

i understand there may be alot of people who may come and collect their parcel but i believe we all come at the timing the were chosen by the store.

so i dont think its really nice of you to be rolling your eyes or giving bad energy when people is coming to collect their item.

please be better. if you feel its too much to handle then stop being a collection point.

Owners of this shop does not adhere to their operating hours stated on google, shopee or lazada. Attempted to collect my parcel on multiple occasions and it wasnt open, parcel was returned to seller because of this. Better not use this location as pickup for your parcels.

Buyers bought products from Lazada, do refrain from self pickup at this store.
Shop Owners seem unpredictable.
They suka suka open and close the shop.
Lazada delivery was there but shop was closed.
I know it is going to be my lucky day when I see this shop open on rare occasions
